snippet.title: KarBOOM Trailer
snippet.description:
Try not to explode in KarBOOM -- a 12-player local multiplayer party game for Windows, Mac & Linux.

Play with up to 4 players on keyboard(s), another 8 using controllers (XBox 360, PS3, PS4, Wii+Nunchuk, Logitech, whatever will work on your OS), bots with different play styles, mutators to change the rules, team play, free for all or a mix of both.

Find out more at http://KarBOOM.net
Help KarBOOM get on Steam: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=185252309
